The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Bindra dad arrested
                                                   Bindra dad arrested
            OUR CORRESPONDENT                      
	Chandigarh: Indias lone individual Olympic gold medal winner Abhinav Bindras father, A.S. Bindra, was arrested late on Thursday by the Delhi police from his residence in Zirakpur, about 15km from here, for failing to repay loans worth crores from banks and financial institutions.         
	The arrest was made by the economic offence wing of the Delhi police following the issuance of a non-bailable warrant on a complaint made by Apple Finance and IndusInd Bank in a Delhi court.                                                                                                                       
